const MYCONSTANT = {
        //Regular Expression
        GET_URL : /(https?:\/\/[^\s]+)/g,
        GET_TEXT : /`(.*?)`/,

        CONTACT: "Contact the developer",
        TERMS : "Terms of service",
        CANCEL:"Cancel",
        TRY:"Try it out",
        PARAMETERS:"Parameters",
        NAME:"Name",
        DESCRIPTION:"Description",
        REQUIRED:"* required",

        POST:"post", 
        PUT:"put",
        GET:"get",
        DELETE:"delete",

        BODY:"body",
        ARRAY:"array",
        STRING:"string",
        INTEGER:"integer",
        FILE:"file",
    }
    export default MYCONSTANT;
